{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sustainability_initiatives", "channel": "recycling_partnerships", "user": "john_doe", "message": "Hey team, I'm thrilled to share that our partnership with the North American recycling facility, based in Nevada, is now official. The agreement was signed in October 2024. We will be sending our end-of-life vehicle batteries to them for processing. This will not only support our zero-emission goals but will also help us recover valuable materials like lithium, cobalt, and nickel for reuse in new battery production. This is a considerable step towards our sustainability goals", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
